# Description ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Functions to build an XLSForm survey.
# Created by Ben Ewing on 2019-08-20

# Functions --------------------------------------------------------------------

# TODO:
# add_choices
#   Desc: A set of choices for the choices page
# add_group
#   Desc: A group. Basically just a valid XLSForm on its own.
# add_repeat_group
#   Desc: A repeat group. Basically just a valid XLSForm to be repeated.
# add_integer
#   Desc: Integer (i.e., whole number) input.
# add_decimal
#   Desc: Decimal input.
# add_range
#   Desc: Range input (including rating)
# add_text
#   Desc: Free text response.
# add_select_one
#   Desc: [options] 	Multiple choice question; only one answer can be selected.
# add_select_multiple
#   Desc: [options] 	Multiple choice question; multiple answers can be selected.
# add_rank
#   Desc: [options] 	Rank question; order a list.
# add_note
#   Desc: Display a note on the screen, takes no input.
# add_geopoint
#   Desc: Collect a single GPS coordinate.
# add_geotrace
#   Desc: Record a line of two or more GPS coordinates.
# add_geoshape
#   Desc: Record a polygon of multiple GPS coordinates; the last point is the same as the first point.
# add_date
#   Desc: Date input.
# add_time
#   Desc: Time input.
# add_dateTime
#   Desc: Accepts a date and a time input.
# add_image
#   Desc: Take a picture or upload an image file.
# add_audio
#   Desc: Take an audio recording or upload an audio file.
# add_video
#   Desc: Take a video recording or upload a video file.
# add_file
#   Desc: Generic file input (txt, pdf, xls, xlsx, doc, docx, rtf, zip)
# add_barcode
#   Desc: Scan a barcode, requires the barcode scanner app to be installed.
# add_calculate
#   Desc: Perform a calculation; see the Calculation section below.
# add_acknowledge
#   Desc: Acknowledge prompt that sets value to “OK” if selected.
# add_hidden
#   Desc: A field with no associated UI element
# add_xml
#   Desc: -external 	Adds a reference to an external XML data file
